1)generating data
compiled with
g++ `pkg-config opencv --cflags --libs` -std=gnu++0x -o test generating_2D_segmentation_data.cpp


2)segmenting data
requires
Eigen (http://eigen.tuxfamily.org/)
CImg.h (included already) (cimg.sourceforge.net)

compiled with
g++ MarkovRandomFieldSegmentation.cpp -L/usr/X11R6/lib -lm -lpthread -lX11 -o mrf -std=gnu++11

